{"tid":1934294,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"重磅！湖人2名球員感染新冠病毒 日前剛打網隊","createTime":"2020-03-20T00:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T05:38:16.000Z","uid":173952,"like":94,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"75c84f76977bf47266fbb7b18ed9c615ad84c87b","tid":1934294,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T00:12:03.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月20日，據著名NBA記者查拉尼亞報導，目前已經有2名洛杉磯湖人隊的球員被檢測出染上了新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n  自從網隊宣佈球隊里4名球員被確診染上新冠病毒之後，湖人隊立刻安排讓球員接受新冠病毒的檢測，因為NBA宣佈無限期停賽之前，網隊的最後一個對手就是湖人隊。<br />\n<br />\n  昨天，湖人隊的大部分球員都已經接受了新冠病毒的檢測。<br />\n<br />\n  今天，著名NBA記者查拉尼亞在Twitter上透露，目前已經有2名洛杉磯湖人隊的球員被檢測出染上了新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n  在這種情況下，湖人隊可能會讓昨天沒有接受新冠病毒檢測的球員接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉，昨天一共有14名湖人隊的球員接受了檢測。<br />\n<br />\n  （羅森）"},{"pid":"d9d46b07cc99fe22586c66557d5b2c3de1d908c7","tid":1934294,"uid":123848,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"皇上奶共派大禮"},{"pid":"9cd1385fed8b842117a02b88c26f6e1ed8790476","tid":1934294,"uid":205684,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T00:13:46.000Z","msg":"唔係James 同AD掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5716f22dd5e94507b922d6b95327a1dfc790ec0a","tid":1934294,"uid":81308,"like":113,"dislike":6,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T00:15:26.000Z","msg":"希望係奶共詹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6a1305ae6fa69d1267e8e5abbd9aa1215fa69d","tid":1934294,"uid":4574,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T00:16:09.000Z","msg":"LBJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f095266326e287e2e914ff243e462b161a6744","tid":1934294,"uid":18220,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"希望唔係Kuzma or AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28d6cd43aed0fd41d05faa2d754ac51f6070c23","tid":1934294,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,